name: Apple iPad (9th Generation): with A13 Bionic chip, 10.2-inch Retina Display, 64GB, Wi-Fi, 12MP front/8MP Back Camera, Touch ID, All-Day Battery Life – Silver
feature_bullets: WHY IPAD — All the essentials in the most affordable iPad, with a beautiful 10.2-inch Retina display, powerful A13 Bionic chip, and an Ultra Wide front camera with Center Stage. Work, play, create, learn, stay connected, and more.,IPADOS + APPS — iPadOS makes iPad more productive, intuitive, and versatile. With iPadOS, run multiple apps at once, use Apple Pencil to write in any text field with Scribble, and edit and share photos. iPad comes with essential apps like Safari, Messages, and Keynote, with over a million more apps available on the App Store.,FAST WI-FI CONNECTIVITY — Fast Wi-Fi keeps you connected at home, work, school, or wherever you go with your iPad.,PERFORMANCE AND STORAGE — The A13 Bionic chip gives you the graphics performance you need. And with all-day battery life, iPad is perfect for playing immersive games and more. Choose from 64GB or 256GB storage options.,APPLE PENCIL AND SMART KEYBOARD — Apple Pencil (1st generation) transforms iPad into an immersive drawing canvas and the world’s best note‑taking device. The Smart Keyboard features a comfortable typing experience and folds into a slim, lightweight cover for protection. Accessories sold separately,10.2-INCH RETINA DISPLAY — With incredible detail and vivid colors, it’s perfect for watching movies or drawing your next masterpiece. True Tone adjusts the display to the color temperature of the room to make viewing comfortable in any light.,UNLOCK AND PAY WITH TOUCH ID — Touch ID is built into the top button, so you can use your fingerprint to unlock your iPad, sign in to apps, and make payments securely with Apple Pay.,FRONT AND BACK CAMERAS — iPad features a 12MP Ultra Wide front camera that supports Center Stage for videoconferencing and selfies. The 8MP Wide back camera is perfect for capturing photos, 1080p HD video, and scanning documents.,LEGAL DISCLAIMERS — This is a summary of the main product features.

feature_bullets: 【2024 Newest Android 12+Strong 2.4G/5G Wi-Fi】 DMOAO tablet adopts the 2024 latest version of Android 12 system and has passed Google GMS. Besides, it supports 802.11ac high-speed dual band and allows you to connect to 2.4g + 5g WiFi networks. The android tablets can give you personalized security systems, lightning fast application launches, super smooth gaming, and stunning multimedia experiences.,【8GB(4+4)RAM+ 64GB ROM+512GB Expand】The Android 12 tablet PC built-in a powerful storage combination of 8GB RAM（4GB+4GB achieved through expansion technology) and 64GB ROM, comes with new generation ultra-high performance and low power consumption 2.0GHz CPU, achieve faster and more stable running and storage speeds. In addition, it can be expanded up to 512GB with a microSD card (card not included) for even more storage.,【6000mAH Battery+Lightweight Metal Body】The D3 tablet is equipped with a 6000mah battery, a single charge can last up to 8 hours, maximize your downtime for reading, browsing the web, watching videos, and listening to music at home and on-the-go. In addition, it is 18% lighter than other tablets on the market, weighing only 430 grams, and at 6 millimeters thick, the tablet is lightweight and portable.,【IPS Display & Dual Speaker】- Equipped with 10.1" IPS 1280x800 HD screen, 5.0MP front camera/5.0MP rear camera, and it include dual-speaker, this android 12 tablet offers you a delightful experience while watching movies, reading books, or making video calls.,【Lifetime Warranty】DMOAO tablet provide Lifetime Warranty service. You will enjoy Lifetime Warranty when you contact DMOAO service through Amazon within 7 days after receiving. We will solve your after-sale problems with the best service attitude and the fastest speed to make you worry-free.

name: Kids Tablet, Android Tablet for Kids 10.1 Inches, 64GB Kids Tablet with Case, Dual Camera, WiFi, Bluetooth, GMS, Kidproof App Pre-Installed, Parent Control, Education, Google, YouTube (Pink)
feature_bullets: 【New Upgraded & Full-Featured Kids Tablet】Up to 30% FASTER AND SMOOTHER.Allwinner quad core CPU 1.6GHz, android 11 OS, 2GB+64GB and support 64GB TF (storing photos, music and videos), dual camera, Wifi, bluetooth and 10in Screen. The upgraded 5000mah battery can up to 10 hours of battery for reading, browsing the web, watching videos, and listening to music, great for road trip or flight,【Perfect Kid Tablets for Educational and Entertaining】IWAWA App is pre-installed on the tablet, which provides thousands of free contents and games suitable for children's age, such as montessori, games, TV, karaoke, Art, painting and so on, that keeps children engaged while fostering their learning. Also, you can download educational apps like YouTube Kids, ABC Mouse, Netflix from Google Play for kids to explore more, A perfect starter tablet for kids,【Easy to Use Parental Control】The children's tablet is equipped with parental control mode, parents can set screen time, set separate profiles for each kid, add or block apps, filter contents, Easily pick and choose what your little one can and can’t have access to as kids grow according to their age,【Childproof Case & Larger Eye Protection Screen】The tablet for kids is equipped with durable child proof case that protects the tablet from scratches, dirt and bumps, drops and dust, The hollow protective case also has the function of heat dissipation. 1280 x 800 IPS touch screen with clear bright screen provides outstanding visual experience and large enough for kids to navigate,【12-Month Warranty】:ABOUT Trayoo, we're committed to delivering the best professional kids tablets and service. All tables for kids have undergone rigorous testing and continuous improvement to ensure superior performance. And if you encounter any problems, Please contact us firstly and our Trayoo Support team is always here to listen and help

name: Android Tablet 10.1" inch, 4G LTE Dual SIM, 16GB RAM,256GB Storage,Supports Extend 1TB, IPS Touchscreen,Dual Camera, WiFi/WLAN/Bluetooth/GPS,TYD-109
feature_bullets: 【Android 13 OS & 16GB RAM 256GB ROM】The TYD-109 android tablet runs on Android 13 system and is loaded with an 16GB RAM（8GB+8GB） and 256GB of ROM for storing all your apps, files, and media. This tablet is perfect for playing large games and loading large data. It has lightning-fast speed and smooth performance. You will find that web pages load without any lagging and apps open in a snap. Whether you're streaming videos, playing games or working on important documents, this tablet handles every task easily.,【10.1 inch FHD IPS tablet + wireless projection + 5MP/13MP Camera】 The tablet has a 10.1 inch 1920*1200 resolution. Wide viewing angle IPS FHD screen, you can enjoy more real and shocking images. It supports wireless projection (not HDMI) for easy connection to a big TV. Face recognition, unlocking is more convenient and intelligent. With 5MP + 13MP camera, microphone, Type-C charging port, dual-band Wi-Fi and BT 5.0, it has everything you need for virtual learning and video calling on the go,【Google GMS Certification & Max-Expandable 1TB】This Tablets is equipped with 256GB ROM Built-in memory, supports 1TB (1024GB) capacity expansion, includes a micro SD slot, allows you to download a lot of applications from Google Play Store and have fun with them. The android tablet has passed the Google GMS certification. You have full access to the latest Google service, such as Google Play, WhatsApp, G-mail, Skype, Disney+, Netflix, YouTube, ZOOM, Google Assistant and more brilliant apps,【2.4G/5G Wifi + 8000mAh + GPS】Tablets with AC dual-band 2.5+5G WiFi, providing an ast Internet experience with less radio interference. 8000mAh and a low-power processor. Achieve up to 10 hours of video battery life. It also has GPS, you can use Google Maps if you download offline maps to your tablet. The 10.1 inch tablet adopts metal body and stylish blue. The smooth touch makes it easy to hold. With a weight of 530g, it is very convenient to carry whether you are working, studying or going out,Compatibility and Better Service The tablet supports google-certified GMS software, which allows you to download a range of android apps from Google apps.If you have any problem with the product, please feel free to contact us. TYD's customer service ensures that you can provide a satisfactory solution

name: 3 in 1 Wireless Microphone for iPhone, Camera, Android, iPad, Mini Microphone, USB C Microphone, iPhone Mic, 2.4G Ultra-Low Delay, Microphone for Video Recording/Vlog/TikTok/YouTube/Interview
feature_bullets: Long-Range Wireless Tranmission: EJCC upgraded 3-in-1 wireless microphone is completely free of wires and is perfect for interviews, video blogs, online meetings, immersive group events and engaging live multiplayer broadcasts. The wireless lavalier microphone works with iPhone, you can simply clip the microphone to your clothes to free your hands, 65 feet of stable reception, and the freedom to record without limitations.,360-Degree HD Sound Pickup: EJCC fully upgraded microphone for iphone built-in active noise reduction chip, remote radio effect is comparable to professional radio equipment, noisy environments can also be realized in high fidelity sound quality. The mini microphone with high sensitivity microphone head, omni-directional sound reception, clear recording of each and every detail of the sound, so that the sound sounds better than the radio.,Applications: EJCC wireless lavalier microphone comes with a 3-in-1 universal receiver, eliminating the need to replace multiple separate interfaces or interface cables. Compatible with Android smartphones, iPhones (including iPhone 15), iPads, laptops, PCs, cameras and more. Wireless microphones, Ideal for bloggers, journalists, Mukbang, fitness instructors, teachers and office workers.,Dual Wireless Microphones & 7 Hours Working: The dual wireless lavalier microphone has a built-in high-capacity rechargeable battery and a low-power chip that provides more than 7 hours of battery life for a day's worth of recording. In addition, this iPhone microphone supports charging while recording. The receiver and cell phone can be charged at the same time via a type-C charging cable.,Easy Autonatic Connection: EJCC mini microphone wireless is easier to set up, simply plug the receiver into your device and press and hold the power button on both the microphone and the receiver and the two parts will connect automatically, no apps or Bluetooth required. Some Android phones and C-type interface devices need to search for OTG in the device settings bar and manually turn on the (OTG) switch to connect to the microphone.,Three Modes:Receiver button to switch modes, green light on behalf of the amplifier mode, it is recommended to use in the speaker; ice blue light on behalf of the camera mode, it is recommended to use in the camera, sound card; blue light on behalf of the cell phone mode, it is recommended to use in the cell phone, tablet, laptop.

name: Kids Tablet, 7 inch Android Tablet for Kids, 6GB RAM 32GB ROM Quad-Core Toddler Tablet with Shockproof Case, Bluetooth, WiFi, Parental Control, 2MP+2MP Dual Camera, GPS, Games (Pink)
feature_bullets: Parental Control for Safe Exploration - The Aiprotablet Kids Tablet comes with a parental control mode that allows you to create and customize profiles for your child's account to provide age-appropriate content. And you can ensure healthy tablet use by setting screen usage hours.,Education and Entertainment in One - The pre-installed iWawa application offers a wide range of age-appropriate content. With Wi-Fi connectivity and access to Google services, parents can download educational apps from the Google Play store. Let your child explore games, media, e-books, drawing, and note-taking for an engaging learning experience.,2024 Newest Model - Our kids tablet comes with 1024x600 IPS touchscreen, GMS certified Android 11 OS, Quad-core processor, 6GB (2+4) RAM, 32GB ROM (up to 128 expandable), WIFI, Bluetooth, 2MP+2MP Dual Camera, FM, GPS. Upgraded battery ensures hours of use, ideal for home or Ideal for home or outdoor travelling.,Durability Meets Convenience - Our tablet cases are made of soft and durable silicone that can withstand accidental drops, bumps and scratches. Ensure reliable protection for your child's device. It features a 360-degree rotatable stand that allows the tablet to be placed horizontally or vertically so your child can study, watch or play games in comfort.,100% Service Guarantee - Our kids tablet comes with 1 years warranty, if it fails, we will replace it for free instead of repairing it. If you have any questions, please contact us and we will reply within 24 hours. Packing List: 1 x Tablet, 1 x Silicone case, 1 x Screen protector, 1 x Type-c cable, 1 x User manual.

name: Amazon Fire HD 8 Kids tablet, ages 3-7. Top-selling 8" kids tablet on Amazon - 2022. Ad-free content with parental controls included, 13-hr battery, 64 GB, Blue
feature_bullets: SAVE UP TO $60 on a full-featured tablet (not a toy) for kids ages 3–7, 1 year of Amazon Kids+, and a Kid-Proof Case with built-in stand, versus items purchased separately.,RESPONSIVE WITH LONG BATTERY LIFE - Features 8" HD display, 2 GB RAM, 32 or 64 GB, up to 1 TB of expandable storage. Now up to 30% faster hexa-core processor compared to Fire HD 8 Kids 10th Generation. All-day battery life - Up to 13 hours of enjoying books, shows, and listening to music.,CONTENT KIDS LOVE - Includes 1 year of Amazon Kids+ - a digital subscription designed for kids to safely learn, grow and explore. On the Fire HD 8 Kids, kids can enjoy thousands of ad-free books, games, videos, apps and more. After 1 year, your subscription will automatically renew every month starting at just $5.99/month plus applicable tax. You may cancel any time by visiting the Amazon Parent Dashboard or contacting Customer Service.,2 YEAR WORRY-FREE GUARANTEE INCLUDED - If the tablet breaks, return it and we’ll replace it for free. Screen made with strengthened aluminosilicate glass and every Fire Kids tablet comes with a sturdy Kid-Proof Case designed to protect against drops and bumps.,NO HASSLE PARENTAL CONTROLS - allows you to use parental controls to filter content based on child's age, set educational goals and time limits, and grant access to additional content from Netflix, Disney+, and Zoom. Parents can manage content for up to 4 child profiles. Kids can't access social media or make in-app purchases without parental approval.,FUN AND EDUCATIONAL CONTENT INCLUDED - Amazon Kids+ content is curated and age-appropriate, so kids can learn, create, and play. Adjustable age filters let you customize the tablet to grow with your child. Plus, it's easy to add content to your child's profile for access to more apps and games.,WITH A STURDY KID-PROOF CASE - What's included: Fire HD 8 Kids (12th Gen) wifi-enabled tablet, Amazon Kid-Proof Case with stand/handle - Amazon power adapter, USB-C (2.0) charging cable, built-in rechargeable battery, and 1-year Amazon Kids+ subscription (auto-renews at applicable rate).,LOVED BY PARENTS: Fire Tablets for Kids have tens of thousands of 5-star ratings.

name: 10 inch Android 13 Tablet, 6GB RAM 64GB ROM 1TB Expand, 2 in 1 Tablets with Keyboard, Case, Mouse, Stylus, 1280x800 IPS Touch Screen, 2.0GHz Quad-Core, WiFi 6, Bluetooth5.0, Dual Camera (Gray)
feature_bullets: The Ideal Portable Workspace - Transform your tablet into a compact and highly-functional workspace. With the accompaniment of a Bluetooth keyboard, wireless mouse, and foldable protective case, you hold the power to instantly switch between tablet and laptop modes. A world of work and learning efficiency is at your fingertips.,Faster Responsive Performance - At the heart of our 10-inch tablet is powerful Android 13.0 with Bluetooth 5.0, 2.4G/5G WIFI6, 6GB RAM, 64GB ROM memory and a 2.0GHz quad-core processor. Expand the storage capacity up to 1TB with an additional microSD card slot to store all the content you need.,Breathtaking Display Experience - Featuring a narrower bezel design, this tablet's 1280x800 resolution FHD IPS display offers a wider viewing area and rich colors, bringing you a better visual experience and ensuring movies are more engaging, notes are clearer, and work is more satisfying.,Long-lasting Battery Life - Armed with a resilient 6000mAh battery, the Android 13 tablet is built for the long haul. Study, work, or play, uninterrupted from dawn till dusk with up to 8 hours of regular operation, and enjoy the additional standby time of up to 12 hours.,Immersive Entertainment Experience - Dual cameras allow you to take HD photos and enjoy clear video calls. Dual speakers bring a better experience to your music, movies and games.The package includes: 1 x 10.1 inch Tablet, 1 x Keyboard, 1 x stylus, 1 x protective case, 1 x protective film, 1 x USB charger, 1 x USB-C cable, 1 x Charger, 1 x user manual.

name: Swivel Keyboard Case for Apple iPad 10.2 inch 9th 8th 7th, iPad Air 3rd and iPad Pro 10.5 2nd Generation: Wireless Rotatable Cover, Pencil Holder, Smart Trackpad, RGB Backlit, Space Gray
feature_bullets: 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐛𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲: edaiser keyboard case is perfectly compatible with iPad 9th Gen (2021, 10.2-inch), iPad 8th Gen (2020, 10.2-inch), iPad 7th Gen (2019, 10.2-inch), iPad Air 3rd Gen (2019, 10.5-inch) & iPad Pro (2017, 10.5-inch) including models A1701, A1709, A2123, A2152, A2153, A2154, A2197, A2198, A2199, A2200, A2270, A2428, A2429.,𝐀𝐝𝐣𝐮𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐕𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐲: Unleash your creativity with the keyboard’s 360° rotation and 180° lay-flat design, effortlessly adapting to your every need.,𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐮𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐜𝐡 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨𝐥𝐬: Experience seamless navigation with the multi-touch touchpad, supporting single, double, and triple-finger gestures for an intuitive and smooth interaction.,𝐈𝐥𝐥𝐮𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐢𝐭𝐲: Illuminate your inspiration with seven captivating backlight colors and three adjustable brightness levels, ensuring precision and comfort in any environment.,𝐔𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐫𝐮𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐏𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞: Stay connected with cutting-edge Bluetooth technology, With a robust rechargeable battery, enjoy up to 90 days of standby time and 180 hours of typing with the backlight off.,𝟑𝟔𝟎° 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 & 𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐥 𝐇𝐨𝐥𝐝𝐞𝐫: Crafted from premium & lightweight ABS plastic, the Edaiser Keyboard provides 360° protection and unmatched durability. The integrated design pencil holder ensures your pencil won't get lost anymore. (Pencil not included),𝐑𝐞𝐟𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐝 𝐓𝐲𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐄𝐱𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞: Elevate your iPad experience with the Edaiser Keyboard – A full row of iPadOS shortcuts and familiar QWERTY layout boost your efficiency and productivity.,𝐀𝐜𝐜𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐈𝐧𝐜𝐥𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐝: 1* edaiser Swivel Series - 102ATS Space Gray; ‎1*User Manual; 1* Type-C to Type-C Cable.

name: NORTH BISON Android Tablet, 10.1 Inch Android 13 Tablet, 6GB RAM 128GB ROM, 1TB Expand, Tablet with 8000mAh Long Battery,Tablet with Dual Camera, WiFi, Bluetooth, HD Touch Screen, GMS Certified-Black
feature_bullets: 【6GB RAM 128GB ROM & Excellent Processor】This 10 inch tablet has 6GB RAM and 128GB storage. You can easily launch apps, watch videos, use learning tools, read e-books, and play games without any lag. It has plenty of storage for apps, photos, videos, and more. You can expand the storage up to 1TB with a MicroSD card (not included), so you won't run out of space.,【GMS Certification】The tablet featuring Android 13.0 operating system,It is certified by GMS, giving you full access to popular services and apps such , WhatsApp, Gmail, Skype, Disney+, Netflix, YouTube, Zoom, Assistant.,【8000mAh High Capacity Battery】The Android tablet has an 8000mAh battery, providing long-lasting performance. A single charge can last up to 16.5 hours, making it perfect for long commutes, travel, reading, watching movies, dramas, and listening to music. It also features a Type-C port for easy charging. The tablet's battery saving features help extend battery life, allowing for longer usage periods without worrying about running out of power.,【Tablet with Protective Case】This 10 inch Android tablet includes a complimentary protective case that is specifically designed for this tablet model. Made from durable materials, the case provides excellent protection against scratches, drops, shocks, and other potential damages. With the included case, you won't need to spend time searching for a separate case to protect your tablet, ensuring that your device remains secure and safe.,【Protective Case 】Our 10 inch android tablet come with multifunctional adjustable protective cases to ensure they are not damaged by drops, scratches, fingerprints, or impacts. Package Includes：1 x Tablet PC, 1 xTablet Case, 1 x Type-C Charging Cable, 1 x User Manual

name: ProCase for iPad 9th Generation 2021/ iPad 8th Generation 2020/ iPad 7th Generation 2019 Case, iPad 10.2 Case iPad Cover 9th Generation -Navy
feature_bullets: Protective case for iPad 10.2 Inch ( 2021 iPad 9th Gen / 2020 iPad 8th Gen / 2019 iPad 7th Gen); Fit iPad Models: A2602 / A2603 / A2604 / A2605 / A2197 / A2198 / A2200 / A2270 / A2428 / A2429 / A2430. It is Not compatible with any other devices. Please check back bottom of your iPad to find the model number,Ultra slim and lightweight hard back design adds minimal bulk while offers your device great protection,The translucent frosted back cover allows you to see the Apple icon through your favorite color, while protects your device against fingerprints and scratches,Classic and professional design; Full access to all features (Cameras, Speaker, Ports and Buttons), but NOT support Smart Keyboard in this case,Support auto Sleep/Wake feature; Magnet secures the case closure, easy snap on and off
